--line-clamp-expanded-height: false; --line-clamp-line-height: undefinedpx;" data-v-b137d6ea="" data-test="UpCLineClamp"><!----> <div id="air3-line-clamp-2" tabindex="-1" class="air3-line-clamp is-clamped"><h2 class="h5 mb-0 mr-2 job-tile-title" data-v-b137d6ea=""><a data-v-b137d6ea="" href="/jobs/Inviting-Research-span-class-highlight-Analyst-span-Agencies-Join-Forces_~018399b41f51e991e8/?referrer_url_path=/nx/search/jobs/" class="up-n-link" data-test="UpLink">Inviting Research <span class="highlight">Analyst</span> Agencies to Join Forces</a></h2></div> <!----></div></div> <div class="job-tile-actions d-flex flex-column" data-v-64a3fdd4=""><!----> <!----></div></div> <div data-v-64a3fdd4="" data-test="JobTileDetails"><!----> <ul class="job-tile-info-list text-base-sm mb-4" data-test="JobInfo"><li data-test="job-type-label"><strong>Fixed price</strong></li> <li data-test="experience-level"><strong>Expert</strong></li> <li data-test="is-fixed-price"><strong class="mr-1">Est. budget:</strong> <strong>$200.00</strong></li> <!----></ul> <div data-ev-sublocation="!line_clamp" class="air3-line-clamp-wrapper clamp mb-3" style="--lines: 2; --line-clamp-expanded-height: false; --line-clamp-line-height: undefinedpx;" data-test="UpCLineClamp JobDescription"><!----> <div id="air3-line-clamp-3" tabindex="-1" class="air3-line-clamp is-clamped"><p class="mb-0 text-body-sm">"Opportunity: Join Our Team as a Research <span class="highlight">Analyst</span> Agency"

Are you a highly motivated and detail-oriented Research <span class="highlight">Analyst</span> agency? We're seeking the perfect fit to gather, analyze, and interpret <span class="highlight">data</span>, offering actionable insights and recommendations vital for our decision-making processes.

Ideal candidates should possess:

• Robust analytical skills 
• A sharp attention to detail 
• The capability to work effectively both independently and as part of a team

Key Responsibilities:

•	Conduct research on various topics including market trends, industry developments, competitor analysis, and customer behavior.
•	Gather and analyze <span class="highlight">data</span> from multiple sources such as databases, surveys, interviews, and secondary research materials.
•	Interpret <span class="highlight">data</span> to identify patterns, trends, and correlations guiding strategic decision-making.
•	Prepare reports, presentations, and materials to effectively communicate research findings and recommendations to stakeholders.
•	Collaborate with cross-functional teams to support business initiatives and research objectives.
•	Assist in developing and implementing research methodologies and tools for enhanced efficiency.
•	Maintain <span class="highlight">data</span> integrity and accuracy throughout the research process for reliable findings.

Qualifications:

•	Bachelor's degree in a related field (Economics, Statistics, Business, or Finance); Master's degree preferred.
•	2+ years of experience in a research or analytical role, preferably in corporate or consulting settings.
•	Proficiency in <span class="highlight">data</span> analysis tools/software such as Excel, SPSS, SAS, R, or Python.
•	Strong analytical skills with the ability to collect, organize, and present information with precision.
•	Excellent written and verbal communication skills to convey complex concepts effectively.
•	Proven ability to work independently, manage multiple projects, and meet tight deadlines.
•	Strong problem-solving skills with a proactive approach to research challenges.
•	Familiarity with research methodologies, quantitative and qualitative analysis techniques, and statistical concepts.

Please Note 
• The set rate is applicable for each milestone, typically lasting between 1 to 2 weeks on average. 
• The overall project is expected to conclude in less than one month. 
• This opportunity is specifically for agencies with the specified expertise; individual applications will 
   not be considered. 
• We warmly welcome agencies from Asia to apply and seize this opportunity


If you believe your agency fits this role and meets the qualifications, we invite you to apply and join us on this exciting journey!</p></div> <!----></div> <div class="air3-token-container" --line-clamp-expanded-height: false; --line-clamp-line-height: undefinedpx;" data-test="UpCLineClamp JobDescription"><!----> <div id="air3-line-clamp-9" tabindex="-1" class="air3-line-clamp is-clamped"><p class="mb-0 text-body-sm">Job Overview:

The Sports Book <span class="highlight">Analyst</span> will be responsible for analyzing various sports books to identify the best odds and betting opportunities. This role requires a keen eye for detail, strong analytical skills, and an in-depth understanding of sports betting markets.

Key Responsibilities:

	•	Odds Analysis:
	•	Review and compare odds across multiple sports books to identify favorable betting opportunities.
	•	Utilize statistical models and software to analyze and predict odds movements.
	•	Market Research:
	•	Conduct thorough research on sports events, teams, and players to inform betting strategies.
	•	Stay updated on sports news, trends, and developments that could impact betting odds.
	•	<span class="highlight">Data</span> Collection and Management:
	•	Collect and maintain accurate records of odds from various sports books.
	•	Use <span class="highlight">data</span> management tools to organize and analyze large datasets.
	•	Reporting and Recommendations:
	•	Generate reports that highlight the best odds and potential betting strategies.
	•	Provide actionable insights and recommendations to clients or internal stakeholders.
	•	Risk Assessment:
	•	Identify and assess potential risks associated with various betting opportunities.
	•	Develop strategies to mitigate risks and maximize profitability.
	•	Collaboration and Communication:
	•	Work closely with other <span class="highlight">analysts</span> and team members to share insights and strategies.
	•	Communicate findings and recommendations clearly to clients or internal teams.</p></div> <!----></div> <div class="air3-token-container" data-v-6a1aa03d="" data-test="TokenClamp JobAttrs"><!----> <span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Analytics</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Gambling</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Sports</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Football</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Entertainment</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Online Financial Trading</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Financial Plan</span></span> <span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="air3-token">

--line-clamp-expanded-height: false; --line-clamp-line-height: undefinedpx;" data-test="UpCLineClamp JobDescription"><!----> <div id="air3-line-clamp-11" tabindex="-1" class="air3-line-clamp is-clamped"><p class="mb-0 text-body-sm">Here is a general description of what I am looking for, if you think you can meet most of the requirements please apply.

A highly experienced professional in the field of <span class="highlight">data</span> science, responsible for leading and managing complex <span class="highlight">data</span> projects, developing advanced analytical models, and deriving actionable insights from large datasets. They play a critical role in shaping the <span class="highlight">data</span> strategy and driving decision-making processes within an organization. Senior <span class="highlight">Data</span> Scientists are expected to possess deep expertise in statistical analysis, machine learning, and <span class="highlight">data</span> engineering, along with strong problem-solving and leadership skills.

Key Responsibilities:

Model Development and Deployment:
Design, develop, and deploy advanced machine learning models to solve complex business problems.
Ensure models are scalable, efficient, and robust, suitable for production environments.
<span class="highlight">Data</span> Analysis and Insights:
Perform exploratory <span class="highlight">data</span> analysis to identify trends, patterns, and anomalies.
Translate complex analytical results into actionable business insights and recommendations.

Project Leadership:
Lead <span class="highlight">data</span> science projects from ideation to implementation, managing timelines, resources, and stakeholder expectations.
Mentor and guide junior <span class="highlight">data</span> scientists and <span class="highlight">analysts</span>, fostering a collaborative and innovative team environment.

Collaboration and Communication:
Work closely with cross-functional teams, including engineering, product management, and business stakeholders, to understand their needs and deliver <span class="highlight">data</span>-driven solutions.
Communicate findings and insights effectively to both technical and non-technical audiences.
Continuous Improvement:

Stay updated with the latest advancements in <span class="highlight">data</span> science, machine learning, and related technologies.
Continuously improve and refine analytical methods, tools, and processes to enhance the overall efficiency and effectiveness of the <span class="highlight">data</span> science team.
Qualifications and Skills:

Experience: 
Typically, 5+ years of experience in <span class="highlight">data</span> science or a related field, with a proven track record of successfully leading <span class="highlight">data</span> projects and developing complex models.
Technical Skills: Proficiency in programming languages such as Python, R, and SQL. Experience with machine learning frameworks (e.g., TensorFlow, PyTorch) and <span class="highlight">data</span> visualization tools (e.g., Tableau, Power BI).
Analytical Skills: Strong understanding of statistical methods, machine learning algorithms, and <span class="highlight">data</span> engineering principles.

Soft Skills: 
Excellent problem-solving, communication, and leadership skills. Ability to work effectively in a team-oriented, collaborative environment.

Remember, I am not expecting you to know everything but the skills you already have are enough for me to consider you as a candidate. I just need you to review the role and qualifications and confirm if you can be taught to do the job. 

Compensation: Opportunity to get hired full-time. 

Please let me know if the role interests you so we can discuss further.

Thank You!

Rakib Uddin</p></div> <!----></div> <div class="air3-token-container" data-v-6a1aa03d="" data-test="TokenClamp JobAttrs"><!----> <span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span class="highlight-color" data-v-6a1aa03d="">Data Mining</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span class="highlight-color" data-v-6a1aa03d="">Data Analytics &amp; Visualization Software</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Statistics</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">pandas</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Python</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Machine Learning Model</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">R</span></span> <span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="air3-token">

--line-clamp-expanded-height: false; --line-clamp-line-height: undefinedpx;" data-test="UpCLineClamp JobDescription"><!----> <div id="air3-line-clamp-19" tabindex="-1" class="air3-line-clamp is-clamped"><p class="mb-0 text-body-sm">We are looking for a <span class="highlight">Data</span> Engineer who will play a crucial role in building, managing, and optimizing our <span class="highlight">data</span> infrastructure. You will be responsible for developing and maintaining robust <span class="highlight">data</span> pipelines, ensuring the reliability and efficiency of <span class="highlight">data</span> flows, and supporting <span class="highlight">data</span> analytics initiatives. The ideal candidate is highly skilled in <span class="highlight">data</span> engineering practices and has a passion for <span class="highlight">data</span>-driven decision-making.

Key Responsibilities
•	Design, develop, and maintain scalable <span class="highlight">data</span> pipelines and ETL processes.
•	Ensure <span class="highlight">data</span> integrity, reliability, and quality by implementing best practices for <span class="highlight">data</span> management and monitoring.
•	Collaborate with <span class="highlight">data</span> scientists, <span class="highlight">analysts</span>, and other stakeholders to understand <span class="highlight">data</span> requirements and deliver solutions that meet business needs.
•	Develop and optimize <span class="highlight">data</span> architectures, databases, and <span class="highlight">data</span> warehouses.
•	Troubleshoot and resolve <span class="highlight">data</span>-related issues, ensuring minimal downtime and high availability of <span class="highlight">data</span> services.
•	Implement <span class="highlight">data</span> security and privacy measures in compliance with relevant regulations.
•	Continuously improve <span class="highlight">data</span> engineering processes and stay updated with the latest industry trends and technologies.

Required Qualifications

•	Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Information Technology, or a related field.
•	3+ years of experience in <span class="highlight">data</span> engineering or a similar role.
•	Proficiency in SQL and experience with relational databases (e.g., MySQL, PostgreSQL).
•	Strong programming skills in languages such as Python, Java, or Scala.
•	Experience with <span class="highlight">data</span> pipeline and workflow management tools (e.g., Apache Airflow, Luigi).
•	Familiarity with cloud <span class="highlight">data</span> platforms (e.g., AWS, GCP, Azure) and big <span class="highlight">data</span> technologies (e.g., Hadoop, Spark).
•	Excellent problem-solving skills and attention to detail.
•	Strong communication and collaboration skills.

Preferred Qualifications
•	Master’s degree in a related field.
•	Experience with NoSQL databases (e.g., MongoDB, Cassandra).
•	Knowledge of <span class="highlight">data</span> visualization tools (e.g., Tableau, Power BI).
•	Familiarity with machine learning frameworks and tools.</p></div> <!----></div> <div class="air3-token-container" data-v-6a1aa03d="" data-test="TokenClamp JobAttrs"><!----> <span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span class="highlight-color" data-v-6a1aa03d="">Data Science</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span class="highlight-color" data-v-6a1aa03d="">Data Management</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span class="highlight-color" data-v-6a1aa03d="">Data Analysis</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span class="highlight-color" data-v-6a1aa03d="">Data Mining</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span class="highlight-color" data-v-6a1aa03d="">Big Data</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">Python</span></span><span data-test="token" class="air3-token" data-v-6a1aa03d=""><span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="">ETL Pipeline</span></span> <span data-v-6a1aa03d="" class="air3-token">
